<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA25">
<l>iṅkiruntu colluvate ṉemperumā ṉeṇṇātē</l>
<l>yeṅkum palitiriyu mettiṟamum - poṅkiravi</l>
<l>līmavaṉat tāṭuvatu meṉṉukkeṉ ṟārāyvō</l>
<l>nāmavaṉaik kāṇaluṟṟa ñāṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being here, what to say about all the manners in which</l>
<l>our father without thinking roams for offerings everywhere</l>
<l>and what for [his] dancing in the cremation wood in boiling night, thus we shall inquire</l>
<l>the time we manage to see him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
